Fetch Yaml Contents

Source: R/formods.R
FM_read_yaml.Rd

Wrapper for read_yaml() to make this function available to modules dependent on formods.

Usage

FM_read_yaml(file)

Arguments

file

yaml file.

Value

List containing the contents of the yaml file.

Examples

res = FM_read_yaml(
   system.file(package = "formods",
                         "templates",
                         "formods.yaml"))

res
